videos.description: Texas guard Elijah Mitrou-Long splits two defenders with a pocket pass to Jaxson Hayes, who rises and slams the dunk.
videos.headline: Texas' Hayes throws down dunk off nifty bounce pass

videos.description: Texas' Jericho Sims slips a defender and throws down the two-handed dunk assisted by Matt Coleman III.
videos.headline: Sims jams home two-handed slam

videos.description: Devin Hutchinson cans an open 3-pointer assisted by Carlik Jones on a broken possession to put Radford up 6.
videos.headline: Hutchinson buries big 3-pointer for Radford

videos.description: Texas' Kerwin Roach II lobs a pass to Jericho Sims who smashes home the dunk with a minute left to play.
videos.headline: Texas regains lead on vicious alley-oop
